https://github.com/boot2docker/osx-installer/releases
Boot2Docker: 
[jcao@jimmy ~]$boot2docker init
[jcao@jimmy ~]$boot2docker up
2014/08/19 17:56:52 Waiting for VM to be started...
...........
2014/08/19 17:57:25 Started.
2014/08/19 17:57:25 To connect the Docker client to the Docker daemon, please set:
2014/08/19 17:57:25     export DOCKER_HOST=tcp://192.168.59.103:2375
[jcao@jimmy ~]$ vi ~/.profile
export DOCKER_HOST=tcp://192.168.59.103:2375
